<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV64">
<l>irukkār moḻiyā ṉeṟiyiḻuk kāmai yulakaḷanta</l>
<l>tiruttā ḷiṇainilat tēvar vaṇaṅkuvar yāmumavā</l>
<l>vorukkā viṉaiyoṭu memmoṭu nontu kaṉiyiṉmaiyiṟ</l>
<l>karukkāy kaṭippavar pōṟṟiru nāmaccoṟ kaṟṟaṉamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With words of ṛgvedic verse the gods on earth bow before the holy foot pair</l>
<l>that measured the world without swerving from the path. We too, suffering</l>
<l>from uncontrolled Karma and from ourselves, like people nibbling nascent</l>
<l>unripe fruit in the absence of ripe fruit, have learned to speak [his] holy names with love.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
